}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Vogler speaks with the institutional authority of a priest (higher power) while maintaining a calm, professional tone (neutral respect). As a representative of the church, his language is formal and direct, emphasizing the spiritual weight of the sacrament. The translation reflects this pastoral gravity and religious solemnity.",
