{
  "social_guidance_summary": "As a priest representing religious authority, Vogler speaks with spiritual gravitas and a sense of responsibility over Salieri’s soul. He maintains a high level of formal respect and compassionate patience, using a pastoral register that combines institutional power with gentle, fatherly persuasion.",
