}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "The speaker, a priest, responds to a direct question from Salieri with a neutral and informative tone. The power dynamic is balanced as they engage in a simple exchange of information. The language remains professional and concise, reflecting the institutional but respectful relationship between a cleric and a member of the court.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "就在维也纳。"
}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Salieri interacts with Vogler as an equal acquaintance, correcting a misconception with a neutral and direct tone. The register is conversational and straightforward, reflecting a professional level of respect without excessive formality or intimacy.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "不是我写的。那是莫扎特。沃尔夫冈·阿玛多伊斯·莫扎特。你知道他是谁吧？"
