{
  "social_guidance_summary": "The speaker and listener are intimate peers engaging in playful banter, resulting in a tone of informal resistance and mock hostility. The roughly equal power and friend relationship allow for a spirited, teasing register where the speaker dismisses the listener's trickery with colloquial language.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "Iram——嫁……Em——嫁给我！不，不！你真是个坏蛋。我才不要嫁给坏蛋呢。还是个这么下流的坏蛋。"
