{
  "social_guidance_summary": "As the Emperor, Joseph speaks with clear authority and confidence, reflecting his higher power. The tone is direct and professional, typical of a patron addressing an artist, balancing formal grace with a straightforward business-like approach. The register is polite yet decisive, maintaining a neutral level of respect while asserting his position.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "好，就这样。言归正传。年轻人，我们要向你委约一部歌剧。你意下如何？"
