}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Sid is in a state of absolute shock and disbelief upon learning the pregnancy was a false alarm after he already quit his career. The roughly equal power and intimate history allow for a blunt, colloquial expression of astonishment. The tone should capture the bitter irony and sudden realization of the situation.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "这可真是见鬼了。"
