{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Paula and Lynette are peers in an adversarial confrontation, resulting in a sharp and defensive tone. The equal power dynamic and neutral respect level allow for a direct, emotionally charged denial. The translation reflects a personal, informal rejection of Lynette's accusation.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "不！才不是那样！"
