{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Paula and Zack are in a heated, equal-power argument where Zack has just insulted her. The low respect level indicates Paula should sound defiant and angry, using blunt language to reject the derogatory label. Her tone should reflect the emotional pain of a romantic interest being unfairly characterized.",
