{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Neil and Knox are close friends and peers, resulting in an equal power dynamic and a casual, informal tone. The conversation is relaxed, using colloquialisms suitable for students. The translation reflects this camaraderie and their shared experience of complaining about school food.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "听着，吃什么都比食堂那些“不明肉类”强。"
