{
  "social_guidance_summary": "The speaker and listener are friends and peers of equal status, calling for an informal and direct tone. The translation should reflect a casual agreement to join a group activity without any formal markers or excessive politeness. A brief, colloquial expression is most appropriate for this friendly exchange.",
