{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Neil and Todd are close friends and equals, allowing for an informal, enthusiastic, and candid tone. The translation should reflect Neil's excitement about his dream and his casual frustration toward his father, using natural language typical of peer-to-peer confidence.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "所以我要去演戏了！打我有记忆起我就一直想尝试。去年夏天我甚至想去参加夏季剧团的试镜，但果不其然，我爸不让我去。"
