  "translation_social_labels_only": "尼尔，如果你父亲不准，你还怎么演戏？"
}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Neil and Todd are close peers with equal status, so the dialogue should be informal and direct. Neil expresses a sense of youthful optimism and slight dismissal of his father's authority, calling for a conversational Mandarin register that sounds like two friends talking privately.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "我得先拿到角色，剩下的到时候再操心。"
