{
  "social_guidance_summary": "As a high-ranking Senator, Gracchus maintains a position of authority while treating the listener as a strategic partner in a high-stakes political alliance. The tone is serious, direct, and transactional, reflecting a neutral respect level while demanding a firm commitment.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "如果元老院给你受审的机会，你会支持他们吗？你必须向我保证。"
