{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Commodus speaks with the absolute authority of an Emperor, exhibiting a sense of ownership over his subjects and the listener. The tone is self-satisfied and commanding, yet reveals a weary intimacy. The language should reflect his high status and entitlement while maintaining a direct, informal register suitable for an intimate setting.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "那声音真悦耳！明天，我要让那些公民——我的子民——回到竞技场。众神在上，我累了。过来睡吧；今晚我们要好好庆祝一番。"
