}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "As a person in a position of absolute power, the speaker uses an authoritative but persuasive tone to strike a deal with the listener. The register is direct and transactional, reflecting a hierarchy where the speaker controls the listener’s fate and property. The language balances a command with the promise of high rewards to ensure compliance.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "在公开场合支持我。只要你这么做，我就让你大富大贵，并还你自由。我会归还你的田产。我知道为了重获自由，你愿意付出任何代价。支持我，你就自由了。好好想想，重获自由后你打算做什么？"
}

{
  "social_guidance_summary": "Proximo maintains a position of higher authority and uses a direct, cautionary tone to warn his ally, Cos, about the escalating danger. The translation should reflect the gravity and urgency of the political climate, treating the warning as a serious reminder of the risks they are taking together.",
  "translation_social_labels_only": "你知道昨晚发生了暴乱。现在动荡又开始了，康茂德还调遣了一个军团。你应该明白自己在做什么……"
}

{
